AI Usage
 
Large language models were used in this project for:

- Generate a preliminary HTML and CSS framework for the user interface to speed up development work.
- Generate JavaScript modules (api.js, ui.js, main.js) as a starting point, followed by their verification and customization.
- Generate the structure of REST API endpoints and implementing routes in Flask.
- Verify the correctness of tests, and listing and implementing any missing ones.
- Generate the visual structure of the README documentation, including table layouts and stylistic elements.
- Review the code for consistency and unnecessary elements.
 
All generated code was reviewed, tested, and manually adjusted. Final decisions regarding the architecture,
database design, and feature scope were made by the developer.